        <div n="X06B002D" type="poem"><head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-headnote-1"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-headnote-2"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-headnote-3"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head>
      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-line-1"> The Suit which humbly You have made&#13;</l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-line-2" rend="flush right"> Is fully and Maturely weigh'd;And as 'tis Your Petition:</l><l n="3" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-line-3"> I do Forgive for well I know</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-line-4" rend="flush right"> Since You're so Bruis'd another BlowWou'd Break the Head of Priscian.</l><l n="5" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-line-5"> 'Tis not my Purpose or Intent</l><l n="6" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-line-6" rend="flush right"> That You shou'd suffer Banishment,I Pardon, now You've Courted</l><l n="7" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-line-7"> And Yet I fear this Clemency</l><l n="8" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-line-8" rend="flush right"> Will come too late to profit theeFor You're with Grief Transported.</l><l n="9" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-line-9"> However this I do Command</l><l n="10" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-line-10" rend="flush right"> That You Your Birch do take in handRead Concord and Syntax-on;</l><l n="11" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-line-11"> The Bays You own are onely Mine</l><l n="12" xml:id="spp-X06B002D-line-12" rend="flush right flush right"> Do You then still Your Nouns DeclineSince You've declin'd────Dan: Jackson.<gap/>X06B002D   </l></lg></div>
